{"id":101232,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/位置艺术：一场有趣的比赛/","date":"2010-08-28T10:42:00Z","modified":"2010-08-28T10:42:00Z","title":"位置艺术：一场有趣的比赛","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/81467/2\">iFanr 爱范儿 ♂专注于拇指设备的小众讨论 &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月27日,  已有 5 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p>诺基亚于 8 月 12 日在 Ovi Blog 发起了一场<a title=\"有趣的竞赛\" href=\"http://blog.ovi.com/2010/08/12/sports-tracker-ovi-competition-launches-now/\">有趣的比赛</a>，利用 Nokia 手机上的 Sports Tracker 软件，将自己的旅行路线变成一幅有创意的图画，目前，<a title=\"获奖作品\" href=\"http://blog.ovi.com/2010/08/26/congratulations-to-our-five-sports-tracker-winners/\">获奖作品</a>已经揭晓：</p>\n<p>第一名：<a href=\"http://www.sports-tracker.com/#/workout/modra/2258pd4ldq0m5ur5\">Vesna</a> ——女孩的脸庞<br />\n<a rel=\"attachment wp-att-17544\" href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543/a-girls-face-sports-tracker3-300x279\"><img title=\"A-girls-face-Sports-Tracker3-300x279\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/A-girls-face-Sports-Tracker3-300x279.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"279\" /></a></p>\n<p>第二名：<a href=\"http://www.sports-tracker.com/#/workout/rchiappe/b61kh84qf4d04m9b\">rchiappe</a> ——奔跑的人（地点：迈阿密市中心）</p>\n<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-17545\" href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543/running-man-in-miami1-300x298\"><img title=\"Running-Man-in-Miami1-300x298\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Running-Man-in-Miami1-300x298.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"298\" /></a></p>\n<p>第三名：<a href=\"http://www.sports-tracker.com/#/workout/karlovric/2sjlf3t86e095db7\">Karlo</a> ——老妇人</p>\n<p><span></span><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-17546\" href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543/old-woman-sports-tracker-294x300\"><img title=\"Old-Woman-Sports-Tracker-294x300\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Old-Woman-Sports-Tracker-294x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"294\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\n<p>第四名：<a href=\"http://www.sports-tracker.com/#/workout/tlfarani/9e9249qs880fhe78\">Tiago</a>—— 奔跑的世界</p>\n<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-17547\" href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543/running-world-sports-tracker-300x250\"><img title=\"Running-World-Sports-Tracker-300x250\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Running-World-Sports-Tracker-300x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>第五名：<a href=\"http://www.sports-tracker.com/#/workout/PaulSmith/btoacejoajae1vh7\">Marek</a>—— 大象</p>\n<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-17548\" href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543/elephant-sports-tracker-300x271\"><img title=\"Elephant-Sports-Tracker-300x271\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/Elephant-Sports-Tracker-300x271.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"271\" /></a></p>\n<p>其实，这个创意最早是一个叫 Starvros 的人提出的，他自称此项活动为“位置艺术”，其意思便是以手机为画笔，视大地为画布，通过自己的行走，来完成一个有创意的“位置图画”，如果大家有兴趣，可以登录他的<a title=\"网站\" href=\"http://www.theworldismycanvas.com/greatevent/\">网站</a>看一下。﻿下面这幅是他最新的作品：</p>\n<p><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-17573\" href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543/postion-art\"><img title=\"postion-art\" src=\"http://www.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/postion-art-360x203.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"360\" height=\"203\" /></a></p>\n<p>如果你有兴趣，是否也愿意身体力行，去做一个“位置艺术家”？</p>\n<hr>\n<p><small>© merlin for <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com\">爱范儿: 拇指资讯小众讨论</a>, 2010. |<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543\">Permalink</a> |<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/17543#comments\">3 comments</a> |<br />\nAdd to<br />\n<a href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http://www.ifanr.com/17543&#038;title=%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%BA%E6%9C%89%E8%B6%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%94%E8%B5%9B\">del.icio.us</a><br />\n<br />\nPost tags: <a href=\"http://www.ifanr.com/tag/nokia-symbian-meego\" rel=\"tag\">Nokia &#038; Symbian &#038; MeeGo</a><br />\n</small></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/1017243/tongji.gif\" /><img src=\"http://img.tongji.linezing.com/997968/tongji.gif\" /></p>\n<p>“要翻墙，<a href=\"http://idangxingdafa.info\" target=\"_blank\">用赛风”</a>.</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[1],"tags":[8800]}